text: Dumitru Ivanov (1 January 1946 – 4 June 2021) was a Moldovan politician. He was member of the Parliament of the Republic of Moldova from 2005 until 2009. He was born Chișinău, Moldova. Ivanov was a member of the Electoral Bloc Democratic Moldova. Ivanov died on 4 June 2021 in Chișinău at the age of 75.Fostul deputat și Președinte al Sindicatului Educaţiei şi Ştiinţei, Dumitru Ivanov a decedat ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Moldovan politicians
